│ known memory aliasing issue. If both are true, we can abort scheduling for this bundle.                                      │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ The following change implements this logic:                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ ```cpp                                                                                                                       │
│ // In BoUpSLP::BlockScheduling::tryScheduleBundle                                                                            │
│ // ...                                                                                                                       │
│   // Check if the bundle is valid for scheduling.                                                                            │
